<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Services - Pet Care Service</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #b77626;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #b97420;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .service-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-container:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .button-container a {
            background-color: #4CAF50; /* Green */
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button-container a:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Explore the variety of services we offer to ensure your pet's well-being and happiness. From daily feeding to grooming and medical care, we have it all covered.</p>

        <!-- Service Packages -->
        <section class="service-container">
            <h2>Service Packages</h2>
            <div>
                <h3>Basic Package - SGD $30/1 Hour</h3>
                <p>Includes scheduled feeding, basic grooming, nail trimming, and cat litter cleaning. Perfect for cost-conscious customers looking for essential pet care.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Medium Package - SGD $50/1.5 Hours</h3>
                <p>Builds upon the Basic Package with added grooming baths, ear, and eye cleaning. Ideal for pet owners wanting to provide extra care within a moderate budget.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Premium Package - SGD $70/2 Hours</h3>
                <p>Covers all the services in the Basic and Medium Packages, plus pet daycare services and basic behavior training. Best suited for those seeking comprehensive care for their pets.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Supplementary Services -->
        <section class="service-container">
            <h2>Supplementary Services</h2>
            <div>
                <h3>Pet Training</h3>
                <p>We offer training sessions from SGD $50 to $150 per session, covering basic commands, behavior correction, and advanced skills. All training is conducted by experienced trainers.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Oral Medication Administration</h3>
                <p>Our trained staff can safely administer oral medication to your pet for just SGD $5 per administration.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Pet Supply Purchase Assistance</h3>
                <p>We can assist with purchasing pet supplies, with a service fee of SGD $10 to $20, plus the cost of goods. Enjoy exclusive discounts on items from our partner pet supply stores.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Pet Birthday Parties</h3>
                <p>We organize pet birthday parties ranging from SGD $200 to $500, including venue decoration, pet-friendly cakes, and treats to make your pet's special day unforgettable.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Grooming Services -->
        <section class="service-container">
            <h2>Grooming Services</h2>
            <div>
                <h3>Ear Cleaning - SGD $10/session</h3>
                <p>Prevent ear diseases with our professional ear cleaning service.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Hair Care - SGD $20/session</h3>
                <p>Maintain your pet’s hair health with our specialized hair care services.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Bathing - SGD $30-$70/session</h3>
                <p>We offer bathing services tailored to your pet’s size and hair length, using products that are safe for their skin.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Nail Trimming - SGD $10/session</h3>
                <p>Keep your pet’s nails in top condition with our nail trimming services.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Professional Grooming & Styling - SGD $40-$100/session</h3>
                <p>Our professional grooming and styling services are customized to your pet’s breed and your preferences.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Medical Services -->
        <section class="service-container">
            <h2>Medical Services</h2>
            <div>
                <h3>Pet Medical Transportation - SGD $25-$100</h3>
                <p>We provide safe transportation for your pet to and from veterinary clinics for vaccinations, sterilizations, and emergency treatments.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Medical Appointment Booking - SGD $10/booking</h3>
                <p>We manage and book all your pet’s medical appointments, ensuring a hassle-free process.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Pet Health Monitoring Package - SGD $100</h3>
                <p>Includes regular physical exams, blood tests, and vaccinations in collaboration with veterinary centers to maintain your pet's health.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/booking">Book Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
